@QuickBite.ApiGateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Gateway health check
GET {{QuickBite.ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/
Accept: application/json

### Through the gateway: list all agents (forwards to delivery-agent-service on 5115)
GET {{QuickBite.ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/agents/activeDeliveries
Accept: application/json

### Through the gateway: list all notifications (forwards to notification-service on 5117)
GET {{QuickBite.ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/notifications/all
Accept: application/json

###
